snippet.title: 96.3 Easy Rock Songs - Best Love Songs Playlist
snippet.description:
Manila's Easy Rock 96.3 is the home of easy listening songs. Easy Rock songs playlist of the best love songs, greatest love songs. 

Click SAVE and enjoy the music of Easy Rock 96.3, as they play your all time favorite ballads, mellow songs and heartwarming love songs. 

Also check out these amazing music playlist for love songs fanatics!

96.3 Easy Rock 90s and 2000s Love Songs
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLplXQ2cg9B_qUgUIuYNy0Re14kye2pLaA

My Favorite Love Songs
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLiy0XOfUv4hFd7T79KZQvy6kr0jIHgxtT

My Favorite Love Songs 2
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLiy0XOfUv4hHOC8nCojwvnOW2vpCrj8gM

Best Mellow Songs of 90s Decade (1990-1994)
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLplXQ2cg9B_r5ALV9l7FS8Kg5FaywG7cO

Best Mellow Songs of 90s Decade (1995-1999)
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLplXQ2cg9B_p6lp_2atJOuJjOsG4oEbpo

Best Mellow Love Songs (2000-2009)
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLiy0XOfUv4hFesQwQFmIMieUdEC1X_f2F

HUGOT Love Songs 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLiy0XOfUv4hG8_CcjuGoWG-lQPpo-dRup

Wave 89.1 DreamSounds. Best of Soul, RnB & Love Songs
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLplXQ2cg9B_qEGl7MHORyPAr7dDzEPbYC

FriendZone Hugot OPM Songs
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLplXQ2cg9B_pWMwwop3fxV1mvW5tPxLUG

Tagalog Love Songs - 80s, 90s and 2000s
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLplXQ2cg9B_o9NOoC6DTh0IM1b5FmyfOS

==

From soft rock favorites like "What about love", "I would do anything for love", "Everything I do", to more softer love songs like "More than you'll ever know", "You" and "In your eyes"... 

Easy Rock or EZ Rocks songs never fails to provide your daily dose of radio friendly love songs....It is like a friend whom you can count on in times when you're happy or when you're mending a broken heart. 

Diva tracks to belt out to like "Through the fire", "I will always love you" or "Hero" to the best male balladeers of all time, singing "Against all odds", "It might be you", "Careless whisper" or "Your song", Easy Rock has it... So feel the love, feel the pain, reminisce and take into a trip down memory lane. 

The best adult contemporary love songs with the best AC artists like Mariah Carey, Celine Dion, Whitney Houston, George Michael, Dan Hill, Christopher Cross, Michael Jackson, Dionne Warwick, Luther Vandross, Stevie Wonder, Natalie Cole, Heart, MLTR - all  in one music playlist. Music that will make you fall in love over and over again. So relax and feel the love of Easy Rock (not EZ Rock, not wrock) but DWRK Easy Rock 96.3, “Less talk, more music.“

----------
Easy Rock 96.3 presents the cream of adult contemporary music from the 70’s and 80’s music in a soothing mix with soft rock hits and rhythmic alternative sounds, while accommodating today’s powerful ballads and lush vocal melodies.

Currently, 96.3 Easy Rock or others say 96.3 EZ ROCK is considered the #1 FM radio station that people listen to at-work or in the office. The radio station is proud of its less talk, more music mantra, accepted widely in public and private offices, as well as drive time radio listeners. The station followed the music format of DWLL Mellow Touch 94.7, which is now playing more of Adult Pop Songs and has changed to Mellow 947 and WRock 96.3, The original Easy Rock station, known as  The Heart of Lite Rock, WROCK....

Aside from 96.3 Easy Rock Manila, they also have provincial stations nationwide playing the best mix of lite rock and ballads, that captivated the hopeless romantic pinoys...
